{"segment":1,"line_start":1,"line_end":50,"dialogues":[{"speaker":"char_chu_liu_xiang","speaker_name":"楚留香","listener":"char_su_xin_da_shi","text":"你还有什么话说？","tone":"悲伤","chapter":11,"line_start":6,"line_end":6},{"speaker":"char_su_xin_da_shi","speaker_name":"素心大师","listener":"char_chu_liu_xiang","text":"无……无……","tone":"颤声","chapter":11,"line_start":8,"line_end":8},{"speaker":"char_chu_liu_xiang","speaker_name":"楚留香","listener":"char_su_xin_da_shi","text":"你已无话可说了么？","tone":"无奈","chapter":11,"line_start":10,"line_end":10},{"speaker":"char_chu_liu_xiang","speaker_name":"楚留香","listener":null,"text":"你听着，无论你是谁，要想吓退我那是在做梦，我迟早要揭破你的秘密，你跑不了的。","tone":"豪迈","chapter":11,"line_start":36,"line_end":36},{"speaker":"char_chu_liu_xiang","speaker_name":"楚留香","listener":null,"text":"瞧她的眼神，必定是有许多话要说的，她说的莫非是吴，那凶手莫非是个姓吴的？","tone":"喃喃","chapter":11,"line_start":48,"line_end":48}],"new_entities":{"characters":[{"id":"char_su_xin_da_shi","name":"素心大师","alias":["女尼","痴尼"],"identity":"乌衣庵的尼姑","faction":null,"role":"npc","archetype":"warrior","rank":"平平无奇","one_line":"乌衣庵的尼姑，掌握重要线索但遭人杀害灭口，临死前留下一个无字的线索。","personality":{"traits":["虚弱","沉默","孤独","执着","悲苦","无助","坚韧"],"speech_style":"微弱断续","temperament":"悲苦"},"relationships":[],"known_skills":[],"related_skills":[],"rag_refs":[11],"source_refs":[{"chapter":11,"line_start":4,"line_end":14,"text":"那女尼胸膛里犹有一丝残余的呼吸，突然张开眼来瞧着楚留香，目光竟突然变得奇异的清澈而明亮。"}]}],"skills":[],"techniques":[],"factions":[],"locations":[],"items":[]},"entity_updates":[{"id":"char_chu_liu_xiang","updates":{"source_refs":[{"chapter":11,"line_start":1,"line_end":50,"text":"楚留香黯然道：你还有什么话说？……我突然仰天而笑，道：你听着，无论你是谁……"}]},"relationship_updates":[]}]}
{"segment":2,"line_start":51,"line_end":130,"dialogues":[{"speaker":"char_chu_liu_xiang","speaker_name":"楚留香","listener":null,"text":"这人又是谁呢？为何来到济南城？……美女虽然有时会嫁给蠢丈夫，但良驹却绝不会被庸人所御，好马选择主人时，那眼光的确要比女子选择丈夫精确得多，至少它不会被男人几句花言巧语就骗过了，也不会瞧得白花花的银子就发晕，而且它选择好一个人时，也时常比女人对丈夫忠心得多。","tone":"喃喃","chapter":11,"line_start":80,"line_end":80},{"speaker":"char_chu_liu_xiang","speaker_name":"楚留香","listener":"char_ai_ma_zhi_ren","text":"朋友可是吃了它的苦头么？","tone":"调侃","chapter":11,"line_start":94,"line_end":94},{"speaker":"char_ai_ma_zhi_ren","speaker_name":"挨马之人","listener":"char_chu_liu_xiang","text":"这匹见鬼的马，凶得紧。","tone":"愤怒","chapter":11,"line_start":96,"line_end":96},{"speaker":"char_chu_liu_xiang","speaker_name":"楚留香","listener":"char_ai_ma_zhi_ren","text":"好花多刺，美人和好马也通常都是难惹的，这句话朋友你日后最好时时牢记在心。","tone":"调侃","chapter":11,"line_start":98,"line_end":98}],"new_entities":{"characters":[{"id":"char_ai_ma_zhi_ren","name":"挨马之人","alias":[],"identity":"被黑衣少年烈马踢伤的过路人","faction":null,"role":"npc","archetype":"warrior","rank":"平平无奇","one_line":"在快意堂外被黑衣少年的烈马踢伤，受到楚留香的调侃。","personality":{"traits":["鲁莽","直率","粗俗","冲动","易怒","无知","淳朴"],"speech_style":"粗鲁","temperament":"暴躁"},"relationships":[],"known_skills":[],"related_skills":[],"rag_refs":[11],"source_refs":[{"chapter":11,"line_start":94,"line_end":96,"text":"还有个人捂着肚子蹲在那里，满脸俱是痛苦之色……那人苦着脸骂道：这匹见鬼的马，凶得紧。"}]}],"skills":[],"techniques":[],"factions":[],"locations":[{"id":"loc_kuai_yi_tang","name":"快意堂","region":"济南","one_line":"济南城中的赌场，由冷秋魂主持，是当地最热闹的赌局场所。","source_refs":[{"chapter":11,"line_start":60,"line_end":112,"text":"还未到快意堂，楚留香就又瞧见了那匹马……屋里虽然灯火通明，却是鸦雀无声。"}]}],"items":[]},"entity_updates":[{"id":"char_chu_liu_xiang","updates":{"source_refs":[{"chapter":11,"line_start":51,"line_end":130,"text":"楚留香回到城里……大步走了进来。"}]},"relationship_updates":[]}]}
{"segment":3,"line_start":131,"line_end":250,"dialogues":[{"speaker":"char_leng_qiu_hun","speaker_name":"冷秋魂","listener":"char_hei_yi_shao_nian","text":"阁下既然要赌，在下自当奉陪，但在下却得先请教阁下的高姓大名，阁下想必不至于吝不见告吧？","tone":"陈述","chapter":11,"line_start":132,"line_end":132},{"speaker":"char_hei_yi_shao_nian","speaker_name":"黑衣少年","listener":"char_leng_qiu_hun","text":"我没有名字。","tone":"淡然","chapter":11,"line_start":134,"line_end":134},{"speaker":"char_leng_qiu_hun","speaker_name":"冷秋魂","listener":"char_hei_yi_shao_nian","text":"阁下既不愿将大名相告，只怕……","tone":"陈述","chapter":11,"line_start":138,"line_end":138},{"speaker":"char_hei_yi_shao_nian","speaker_name":"黑衣少年","listener":"char_leng_qiu_hun","text":"只怕怎样？","tone":"疑问","chapter":11,"line_start":140,"line_end":140},{"speaker":"char_leng_qiu_hun","speaker_name":"冷秋魂","listener":"char_hei_yi_shao_nian","text":"这里的规矩，是不与陌生人赌的……","tone":"陈述","chapter":11,"line_start":142,"line_end":142},{"speaker":"char_leng_qiu_hun","speaker_name":"冷秋魂","listener":"char_hei_yi_shao_nian","text":"但阁下远道而来，在下也不能令阁下失望。","tone":"无奈","chapter":11,"line_start":144,"line_end":144},{"speaker":"char_hei_yi_shao_nian","speaker_name":"黑衣少年","listener":"char_leng_qiu_hun","text":"那很好。","tone":"淡然","chapter":11,"line_start":148,"line_end":148},{"speaker":"char_leng_qiu_hun","speaker_name":"冷秋魂","listener":"char_hei_yi_shao_nian","text":"却不知阁下要赌什么？","tone":"疑问","chapter":11,"line_start":150,"line_end":150},{"speaker":"char_hei_yi_shao_nian","speaker_name":"黑衣少年","listener":"char_leng_qiu_hun","text":"就赌骰子。","tone":"陈述","chapter":11,"line_start":152,"line_end":152},{"speaker":"char_leng_qiu_hun","speaker_name":"冷秋魂","listener":"char_hei_yi_shao_nian","text":"赌注……","tone":"疑问","chapter":11,"line_start":154,"line_end":154},{"speaker":"char_leng_qiu_hun","speaker_name":"冷秋魂","listener":"char_hei_yi_shao_nian","text":"阁下要以这玉璧来赌什么？","tone":"淡然","chapter":11,"line_start":160,"line_end":160},{"speaker":"char_hei_yi_shao_nian","speaker_name":"黑衣少年","listener":"char_leng_qiu_hun","text":"赌你。","tone":"淡然","chapter":11,"line_start":162,"line_end":162},{"speaker":"char_leng_qiu_hun","speaker_name":"冷秋魂","listener":"char_hei_yi_shao_nian","text":"赌我？我冷秋魂有如此值钱么？","tone":"大笑","chapter":11,"line_start":164,"line_end":164},{"speaker":"char_hei_yi_shao_nian","speaker_name":"黑衣少年","listener":"char_leng_qiu_hun","text":"我若胜了，你便跟我走。","tone":"陈述","chapter":11,"line_start":166,"line_end":166},{"speaker":"char_leng_qiu_hun","speaker_name":"冷秋魂","listener":"char_hei_yi_shao_nian","text":"好！我赌了。","tone":"激动","chapter":11,"line_start":168,"line_end":168},{"speaker":"char_leng_qiu_hun","speaker_name":"冷秋魂","listener":"char_hei_yi_shao_nian","text":"骰子的赌法也有许多种，阁下……","tone":"陈述","chapter":11,"line_start":174,"line_end":174},{"speaker":"char_hei_yi_shao_nian","speaker_name":"黑衣少年","listener":"char_leng_qiu_hun","text":"赌小，点子少的为胜。","tone":"陈述","chapter":11,"line_start":176,"line_end":176},{"speaker":"char_leng_qiu_hun","speaker_name":"冷秋魂","listener":"char_hei_yi_shao_nian","text":"赌大赌小，都是一样的，阁下请。","tone":"微笑","chapter":11,"line_start":178,"line_end":178},{"speaker":"char_hei_yi_shao_nian","speaker_name":"黑衣少年","listener":"char_leng_qiu_hun","text":"你先摇。","tone":"淡然","chapter":11,"line_start":180,"line_end":180},{"speaker":"char_leng_qiu_hun","speaker_name":"冷秋魂","listener":"char_hei_yi_shao_nian","text":"同点……","tone":"疑问","chapter":11,"line_start":182,"line_end":182},{"speaker":"char_hei_yi_shao_nian","speaker_name":"黑衣少年","listener":"char_leng_qiu_hun","text":"同点作和。","tone":"陈述","chapter":11,"line_start":184,"line_end":184},{"speaker":"char_leng_qiu_hun","speaker_name":"冷秋魂","listener":"char_hei_yi_shao_nian","text":"好。","tone":"陈述","chapter":11,"line_start":186,"line_end":186},{"speaker":"char_hei_yi_shao_nian","speaker_name":"黑衣少年","listener":"char_leng_qiu_hun","text":"果然不错。","tone":"淡然","chapter":11,"line_start":208,"line_end":208},{"speaker":"char_leng_qiu_hun","speaker_name":"冷秋魂","listener":"char_hei_yi_shao_nian","text":"阁下请。","tone":"微笑","chapter":11,"line_start":210,"line_end":210},{"speaker":"char_hei_yi_shao_nian","speaker_name":"黑衣少年","listener":"char_leng_qiu_hun","text":"好。","tone":"陈述","chapter":11,"line_start":212,"line_end":212},{"speaker":"char_hei_yi_shao_nian","speaker_name":"黑衣少年","listener":"char_leng_qiu_hun","text":"我六粒骰子只有一点，你输了……","tone":"淡然","chapter":11,"line_start":232,"line_end":232},{"speaker":"char_leng_qiu_hun","speaker_name":"冷秋魂","listener":"char_hei_yi_shao_nian","text":"这不算，这样自然不算。","tone":"激动","chapter":11,"line_start":234,"line_end":234},{"speaker":"char_hei_yi_shao_nian","speaker_name":"黑衣少年","listener":"char_leng_qiu_hun","text":"你想赖？","tone":"冷笑","chapter":11,"line_start":236,"line_end":236},{"speaker":"char_hei_yi_shao_nian","speaker_name":"黑衣少年","listener":"char_leng_qiu_hun","text":"你输了，跟我走吧！","tone":"冷笑","chapter":11,"line_start":244,"line_end":244},{"speaker":"char_chu_liu_xiang","speaker_name":"楚留香","listener":null,"text":"两位都请慢走，在下也很想和这位朋友赌上一赌。","tone":"陈述","chapter":11,"line_start":246,"line_end":246}],"new_entities":{"characters":[{"id":"char_leng_qiu_hun","name":"冷秋魂","alias":[],"identity":"快意堂赌局主人","faction":null,"role":"npc","archetype":"warrior","rank":"炉火纯青","one_line":"快意堂赌局的主人，精通骰子手法，被黑衣少年击败后险遭带走。","personality":{"traits":["贪婪","狡诈","圆滑","精明","胆小","见风使舵","势利"],"speech_style":"圆滑多变","temperament":"滑头"},"relationships":[],"known_skills":[],"related_skills":[],"rag_refs":[11],"source_refs":[{"chapter":11,"line_start":116,"line_end":170,"text":"冷秋魂的脸上已无丝毫血色，目光中又是惊慌，又是恐惧……好！我赌了。"}]},{"id":"char_hei_yi_shao_nian","name":"黑衣少年","alias":["黑斗篷少年"],"identity":"神秘的黑衣少年","faction":null,"role":"npc","archetype":"warrior","rank":"出神入化","one_line":"神秘的黑衣少年，以六尺长鞭和骰子手法震慑快意堂，寻找冷秋魂的来历不明的高手。","personality":{"traits":["冷漠","孤傲","神秘","坚强","冷酷","暴躁","急躁"],"speech_style":"冷漠尖锐短促","temperament":"冷酷"},"relationships":[],"known_skills":[],"related_skills":[],"rag_refs":[11],"source_refs":[{"chapter":11,"line_start":124,"line_end":136,"text":"他竟是个少年，黑斗篷里，是一身黑色的紧身衣，黑腰带，黑马靴，黑色的小牛皮手套，手里紧握着黑色的长鞭，只有一张脸是苍白的，苍白得可怕。"}]}],"skills":[],"techniques":[],"factions":[],"locations":[],"items":[{"id":"item_yu_bi","name":"玉璧","type":"special","owner":null,"one_line":"黑衣少年用作赌注的绝世宝玉，光泽温良毫无瑕疵。","description":"灯光下只见这玉璧光泽温良，毫无瑕疵，就连楚留香一生中都未见过这么完美的宝玉，就连传说中那足以倾国的和氏璧也未必能比这玉璧强胜多少。","effects":[],"origin":"未知","rarity":"稀世珍品","related_characters":["char_chu_liu_xiang","char_hei_yi_shao_nian","char_leng_qiu_hun"],"related_skills":[],"rag_refs":[11],"source_refs":[{"chapter":11,"line_start":156,"line_end":158,"text":"灯光下，只见这玉璧光泽温良，毫无瑕疵，就连楚留香，一生中都未见过这么完美的宝玉。就连传说中那足以倾国的和氏璧，只怕也未必能比这玉璧强胜多少。"}]}]},"entity_updates":[{"id":"char_chu_liu_xiang","updates":{"source_refs":[{"chapter":11,"line_start":131,"line_end":250,"text":"楚留香从侧面望过去，只见他鼻梁削直……突然听一人悠悠道：两位都请慢走。"}]},"relationship_updates":[]},{"id":"char_leng_qiu_hun","updates":{"source_refs":[{"chapter":11,"line_start":131,"line_end":250,"text":"冷秋魂道：阁下既然要赌，在下自当奉陪……砰的一声，冷秋魂已将宝盖放在桌上。"}]},"relationship_updates":[]}]}
{"segment":4,"line_start":251,"line_end":346,"dialogues":[{"speaker":"char_leng_qiu_hun","speaker_name":"冷秋魂","listener":null,"text":"张兄既然也要来赌，那太好了，简直太好了。","tone":"欣喜","chapter":11,"line_start":258,"line_end":258},{"speaker":"char_chu_liu_xiang","speaker_name":"楚留香","listener":"char_hei_yi_shao_nian","text":"阁下是从沙漠上来的吧？","tone":"调侃","chapter":11,"line_start":264,"line_end":264},{"speaker":"char_hei_yi_shao_nian","speaker_name":"黑衣少年","listener":"char_chu_liu_xiang","text":"你是什么人？","tone":"惊讶","chapter":11,"line_start":266,"line_end":266},{"speaker":"char_chu_liu_xiang","speaker_name":"楚留香","listener":"char_hei_yi_shao_nian","text":"我也和阁下一样，忘记了名字。","tone":"调侃","chapter":11,"line_start":268,"line_end":268},{"speaker":"char_hei_yi_shao_nian","speaker_name":"黑衣少年","listener":"char_chu_liu_xiang","text":"你要赌，好！赌什么？","tone":"疑问","chapter":11,"line_start":270,"line_end":270},{"speaker":"char_chu_liu_xiang","speaker_name":"楚留香","listener":"char_hei_yi_shao_nian","text":"骰子，自然还是骰子，自然还是少的为胜。","tone":"调侃","chapter":11,"line_start":272,"line_end":272},{"speaker":"char_hei_yi_shao_nian","speaker_name":"黑衣少年","listener":"char_chu_liu_xiang","text":"赌注——","tone":"疑问","chapter":11,"line_start":276,"line_end":276},{"speaker":"char_chu_liu_xiang","speaker_name":"楚留香","listener":"char_hei_yi_shao_nian","text":"阁下若是输了，在下自然少不得要将这玉璧带回去，这位冷公子自然也不必跟阁下走了，除此之外，在下还得问阁下几句话。","tone":"陈述","chapter":11,"line_start":278,"line_end":278},{"speaker":"char_hei_yi_shao_nian","speaker_name":"黑衣少年","listener":"char_chu_liu_xiang","text":"你若输了呢？","tone":"疑问","chapter":11,"line_start":282,"line_end":282},{"speaker":"char_chu_liu_xiang","speaker_name":"楚留香","listener":"char_hei_yi_shao_nian","text":"在下若输了，就将阁下一心想知道的那件事，告诉阁下。","tone":"淡然","chapter":11,"line_start":284,"line_end":284},{"speaker":"char_hei_yi_shao_nian","speaker_name":"黑衣少年","listener":"char_chu_liu_xiang","text":"你怎么知道我想问什么？","tone":"惊讶","chapter":11,"line_start":288,"line_end":288},{"speaker":"char_chu_liu_xiang","speaker_name":"楚留香","listener":"char_hei_yi_shao_nian","text":"说不定是知道的。","tone":"调侃","chapter":11,"line_start":290,"line_end":290},{"speaker":"char_hei_yi_shao_nian","speaker_name":"黑衣少年","listener":"char_chu_liu_xiang","text":"好，我赌了。","tone":"陈述","chapter":11,"line_start":294,"line_end":294},{"speaker":"char_chu_liu_xiang","speaker_name":"楚留香","listener":"char_hei_yi_shao_nian","text":"我早就知道阁下要赌的。","tone":"调侃","chapter":11,"line_start":296,"line_end":296},{"speaker":"char_hei_yi_shao_nian","speaker_name":"黑衣少年","listener":"char_chu_liu_xiang","text":"我骰子已掷过，你可要我再照样掷一次？","tone":"疑问","chapter":11,"line_start":298,"line_end":298},{"speaker":"char_chu_liu_xiang","speaker_name":"楚留香","listener":"char_hei_yi_shao_nian","text":"不必了。","tone":"陈述","chapter":11,"line_start":300,"line_end":300},{"speaker":"char_leng_qiu_hun","speaker_name":"冷秋魂","listener":"char_chu_liu_xiang","text":"张兄莫要忘记，那位朋友掷的是一点。","tone":"焦急","chapter":11,"line_start":304,"line_end":304},{"speaker":"char_chu_liu_xiang","speaker_name":"楚留香","listener":"char_leng_qiu_hun","text":"我知道。","tone":"淡然","chapter":11,"line_start":308,"line_end":308},{"speaker":"char_chu_liu_xiang","speaker_name":"楚留香","listener":"char_hei_yi_shao_nian","text":"我六粒骰子一点都没有，阁下恐怕是输了。","tone":"微笑","chapter":11,"line_start":328,"line_end":328},{"speaker":"char_leng_qiu_hun","speaker_name":"冷秋魂","listener":null,"text":"不错不错，六粒骰子连一点都没有，妙极妙极，简直太妙了。","tone":"大笑","chapter":11,"line_start":332,"line_end":332}],"new_entities":{"characters":[],"skills":[],"techniques":[],"factions":[],"locations":[{"id":"loc_wu_yi_an","name":"乌衣庵","region":"济南","one_line":"济南城外的尼姑庵，素心大师修行之所，后被大火烧毁。","source_refs":[{"chapter":11,"line_start":18,"line_end":56,"text":"楚留香走出乌衣庵……那乌衣庵竟已化为一片火海。"}]}],"items":[]},"entity_updates":[{"id":"char_chu_liu_xiang","updates":{"source_refs":[{"chapter":11,"line_start":251,"line_end":346,"text":"悠然的语声，淡淡的微笑，不是楚留香是谁？……六粒骰子竟都变成了粉末落下。"}]},"relationship_updates":[]},{"id":"char_hei_yi_shao_nian","updates":{"source_refs":[{"chapter":11,"line_start":251,"line_end":346,"text":"那少年海般深沉、刀般锐利的目光，已盯在楚留香脸上……那黑衣少年面色惨白。"}]},"relationship_updates":[]},{"id":"char_leng_qiu_hun","updates":{"source_refs":[{"chapter":11,"line_start":251,"line_end":346,"text":"冷秋魂如蒙大赦，立刻展颜笑道……冷秋魂终于忍不住跳了起来，拍手笑道。"}]},"relationship_updates":[]}]}
